Legacy continued for a moment, examining the strange scans from
Marauder, his single optic pulsing as he watched the information
scroll across his screen.

"Lord Perseus." Legacy intoned over the Maximal frequency, "What is to
be the disposition of the other Minion that we still have in custody.
No doubt at some point Marauder will return to reacquire his soldier."

Legacy turned to Talon, "What is the intruder's status?"

(TAG)

Preston
